In 6.5 EIL, for the variable "Eligible for central bank funding indicator" we use two different abbreviations in entities INSTRMNT and SCRTY_EXCHNG_TRDBL_DRVTV, see below:

INSTRMNT (Correct)<br>
![image](/uploads/a43d81347e1252b73ba0e5b125964632/image.png){width=220 height=101}

SCRTY_EXCHNG_TRDBL_DRVTV (Incorrect)<br>
![image](/uploads/8285660fc26484d0168966519a9cfa5f/image.png){width=307 height=122}
